subject: some new clips on YouTube
author: ejspinn
full_text:
http://www.youtube.com/user/ParaSpinnProductions

I uploaded a bunch of new clips from a restaurant we were at.  it supposedly had maffia ties and blah blah blah....

We kept getting a "Nate" come thru, but nobody knows any Nate except Nathan one of the employees there. Who got sick during the session.  EMF levels were off the hook there with a weird pulsing of EMF on 4 k2 meters all at same time. But the radio kept saying his name was Nate.  We get a couple cuss words, a few short sentances. I didn't upload it yet but the box went around the table saying are names in order it was kinda neat.

Is it easier to view them there on Youtube or upload them here and take up space?  Let me know.  Most everybody knows how to navigate youtube and if your on several yahoo groups (like most of us) it's easier to just link them to there instead or uploading the same files several times?
